{"tid":1745430,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"點解香港一般市面賣嘅啤酒都係lager","createTime":"2019-11-22T08:13:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T12:56:27.000Z","uid":22604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f8dc79021b34be21e3869d8586c5f3d41eadd265","tid":1745430,"uid":22604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:13:58.000Z","msg":"一般超市、便利店，差唔多全部啤酒都係lager，除咗有少少guinness嗰類stout 或者 porter<br />\n但鬼佬幾興飲嗰啲pale ale、APA、IPA 就好少見，剩係喺灣仔一間惠康見過<br />\n有無話係咩原因？"},{"pid":"eef5a5d9034cdeb77f6819d16d7851d2c8b18709","tid":1745430,"uid":197393,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:14:53.000Z","msg":"//馮驊無講過票站持續三小時有混亂，即停止選舉！絕對無講過。係建制派send出唻嘅假訊息！<br />\n<br />\n建制派想黃絲盡早投票，等佢哋盡早知道邊啲區需要谷票！中銀無出memo叫人12點前投，同鄉會無send SMS叫人11點前投，全部都係假！<br />\n大家正正常咁投就得，咪俾建制得逞！<br />\n<br />\n馮驊真正講嘅係如投票當日出現事故，但可一個半小時內恢復投票，便會補時繼續進行投票，但如果受影響時間多於一個半小時，投票將會押後一星期再舉行投票！//"},{"pid":"4cee50e9e422639e8e15c48554294a0d2e116d91","tid":1745430,"uid":58147,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T09:06:14.000Z","msg":"Citysuper都有好多。<br />\n不過好貴。"},{"pid":"e100f5b23095f17d6bcd9e876a71916c87236ba1","tid":1745430,"uid":256514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T09:08:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4085697daf2fad8b252eb0b6077c0cdf7c0c976b","tid":1745430,"uid":22604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e100f5b23095f17d6bcd9e876a71916c87236ba1","tid":1745430,"uid":256514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T09:08:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T09:23:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7b208bd2e711ee6382817a738fb791e4009bcf3","tid":1745430,"uid":22604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4cee50e9e422639e8e15c48554294a0d2e116d91","tid":1745430,"uid":58147,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T09:06:14.000Z","msg":"Citysuper都有好多。<br />\n不過好貴。"